.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Browse and search text files, follow changes.
.SS Goals
.IP \[bu] 2
Create a file browser with only the most common features
.IP \[bu] 2
Keep it simple, keep it friendly
.SS Features
.IP \[bu] 2
